Schema omt

Table Comment
CustomBlockDTO  Custom blocks that should be displayed additionally at selected extension points. 
CustomMenuItemDTO  Custom main menu items that should be displayed additionally. 
CustomOrderTabDTO  Custom order detail tabs that should be displayed additionally. 
CustomPropertyPresentationDTO  Properties that should be displayed in a custom block. 
FeatureToggleDTO  A list of feature-toggles to globally enable or disable features in the OMT. 
PresentationType  Presentations that properties can be displayed in.
